Vivek Wadhwa, director of research 
at Duke University's Center for Entrepreneurship and a Bloomberg
contributor, talks about the outlook for Yahoo! Inc.       Wadhwa also discusses the possibility of an initial public 
offering by Facebook Inc. He speaks with Emily Chang and Cory 
Johnson on Bloomberg Television's "Bloomberg West." (Source: 
Bloomberg)  Running time 06:11
 